{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/devops/docker-mysql","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"author":"Inkyung"}},"markdownRemark":{"fields":{"slug":"/devops/docker-mysql"},"id":"ac2c3596-617d-5ab9-8616-f08d4b9510fe","excerpt":"1. mysql 컨테이너 생성 및 실행  명령어를 통해 컨테이너의 생성과 실행을 동시에 진행한다. 옵션 -d \n데몬 프로세스로 실행한다. -p…","html":"<h2 id=\"1-mysql-컨테이너-생성-및-실행\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-mysql-%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%84%88-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1-%EB%B0%8F-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89\" aria-label=\"1 mysql 컨테이너 생성 및 실행 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. mysql 컨테이너 생성 및 실행</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">docker run</code> 명령어를 통해 컨테이너의 생성과 실행을 동시에 진행한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ docker run -d -p <span class=\"token variable\">${호스트에서 접근 할 포트}</span>:3306 --name <span class=\"token variable\">${컨테이너 이름}</span> -e <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\">${PASSWORD}</span> -v <span class=\"token variable\">${로컬 호스트의 저장소 경로}</span>:/var/lib/mysql mysql\n<span class=\"token comment\"># e.g. docker run -d -p 3306:3306 --name mysql-db -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=password -v /Users/inkyung/datadir:/var/lib/mysql mysql</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"옵션\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%98%B5%EC%85%98\" aria-label=\"옵션 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>옵션</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>-d</strong> <br/>\n데몬 프로세스로 실행한다.</li>\n<li><strong>-p ${호스트에서 접근 할 포트}:${컨테이너의 포트}</strong> <br/>\n호스트에서 ${호스트에서 접근 할 포트}로 접근하면 ${컨테이너의 포트}의 컨테이너로 접근하게 된다.</li>\n<li><strong>-e MYSQL<em>ROOT</em>PASSWORD=${PASSWORD}</strong> <br/>\nMYSQL<em>ROOT</em>PASSWORD 이름으로 환경 변수 값을 지정한다.</li>\n<li><strong>-v ${로컬 호스트의 저장소 경로}:/var/lib/mysql</strong> <br/>\n데이터 볼륨 옵션으로, ${로컬 호스트의 저장소 경로}를 mysql의 저장소 경로에 마운트 하도록 설정한다. <br/>\n이 옵션을 설정하지 않으면 데이터 디렉토리가 컨테이너 내부에 생성되어 컨테이너 삭제시 저장소도 함께 지워지게 된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-컨테이너-접속\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%84%88-%EC%A0%91%EC%86%8D\" aria-label=\"2 컨테이너 접속 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 컨테이너 접속</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ docker <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">exec</span> -it <span class=\"token variable\">${CONTAINER_NAME}</span> <span class=\"token function\">bash</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># docker exec -it mysql-db bash</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>패스워드는 위 컨테이너 생성 및 실행 명령어에서 지정한 <code class=\"language-text\">MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD</code>환경 변수 값을 입력한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"3-mysql-서버-접속\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-mysql-%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84-%EC%A0%91%EC%86%8D\" aria-label=\"3 mysql 서버 접속 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. mysql 서버 접속</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ mysql -u root -p </code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"4-mysql-기본-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-mysql-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"4 mysql 기본 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. mysql 기본 설정</h2>\n<h3 id=\"유저-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9C%A0%EC%A0%80-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"유저 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>유저 생성</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">create</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">user</span> <span class=\"token string\">'${USER_NAME}'</span><span class=\"token variable\">@'${HOST}'</span> identified <span class=\"token keyword\">by</span> <span class=\"token string\">'${USER_PASSWORD}'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// e.g. create user 'inkyung'@'%' identified by 'password';</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"유저-권한-부여\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9C%A0%EC%A0%80-%EA%B6%8C%ED%95%9C-%EB%B6%80%EC%97%AC\" aria-label=\"유저 권한 부여 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>유저 권한 부여</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">create</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">user</span> <span class=\"token string\">'${USER_NAME}'</span><span class=\"token variable\">@'${HOST}'</span> identified <span class=\"token keyword\">by</span> <span class=\"token string\">'${USER_PASSWORD}'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// e.g. create user 'inkyung'@'%' identified by 'password';</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"데이터베이스-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0%EB%B2%A0%EC%9D%B4%EC%8A%A4-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"데이터베이스 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>데이터베이스 생성</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">create</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">database</span> ${DB_NAME} <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">character</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">set</span> utf8<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<br/>\n<h2 id=\"참고\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"참고 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://jmlim.github.io/docker/2019/07/30/docker-mysql-setup/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Docker를 통한 MySQL 설치하기 by 기억하기 위한 개발노트</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://linux.systemv.pe.kr/docker-%EC%97%90-volumes-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80-%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">DOCKER 에 VOLUMES 추가 하기 by Voyager of Linux</a></li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/devops/docker-mysql/#1-mysql-%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%84%88-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1-%EB%B0%8F-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89\">1. mysql 컨테이너 생성 및 실행</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/devops/docker-mysql/#%EC%98%B5%EC%85%98\">옵션</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/devops/docker-mysql/#2-%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%84%88-%EC%A0%91%EC%86%8D\">2. 컨테이너 접속</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/devops/docker-mysql/#3-mysql-%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84-%EC%A0%91%EC%86%8D\">3. mysql 서버 접속</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/devops/docker-mysql/#4-mysql-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\">4. mysql 기본 설정</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/devops/docker-mysql/#%EC%9C%A0%EC%A0%80-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\">유저 생성</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/devops/docker-mysql/#%EC%9C%A0%EC%A0%80-%EA%B6%8C%ED%95%9C-%EB%B6%80%EC%97%AC\">유저 권한 부여</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/devops/docker-mysql/#%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0%EB%B2%A0%EC%9D%B4%EC%8A%A4-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\">데이터베이스 생성</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/devops/docker-mysql/#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\">참고</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"mysql 컨테이너 생성하기","date":"July 27, 2020","category":"Docker","tags":["Docker","mysql"],"featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"original":{"src":"/static/thumbnail-be4ce8e8da1055bc5c00f1a652562673.png","width":1200,"height":400}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/devops/docker-mysql","previous":{"id":"81cf666e-46b8-5c2c-9227-ca46b3812c09","fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/programers-level1-js-1"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[JS] Level1 문제 풀기 - 1","tags":["Prog